	<BackstoryDef ParentName="CFAR_Mercenary">
		<defName>CFAR_CivilMercenary1</defName>
		<title>quickdraw</title>
		<titleShort>quickdraw</titleShort>
		<description>Words of the law were never absolute to [PAWN_nameDef]. [PAWN_pronoun] earned a reputation for shooting first and asking questions later—a dependable kind of loose cannon. And to be fair, none of [PAWN_possessive] employers ever hired [PAWN_objective] to ask questions first.</description>
